<br>
Well, personally I wouldn't like a pure PvP game. I do play EQ and I think the game has an excellent balance. Those that play on the PvP servers dont seem to complain and people like me on the regular servers do quite well. As for how boring EQ is, I can see how that might be if you dont interact well with others or have been playing a long time and have grown out of it, but IMO Everquest, in general, has a friendly player base and adequate things to do(especially with all the newbie quests its not nearly as hard to get through the first 20 levels). The only downside I find worth mentioning is that all the servers are pretty aged, meaning its a pretty daunting task for a new player to start out at lvl 1 and hope to aspire to join a first class raiding Guild(One reason im looking forward to the PS2 port).<br>
<br>
Yes leveling does take a while, but it gives you time for your character to mature. If you were allowed to zoom through the levels you would reach the 40's and have a character with a very low attack rating or deplorable skill in spell casting that would make reaching such a high level so quickly pointless because you will only be stuck sitting around working those skills up. Also what would be the point of a persistent world if you are able to conquer everything in a few days? I would take the excitement of discovery and earning my way through a game over self gratification any day.<br>
<br>
PS: I find it strange to see someone named Negafen so opposed to EQ, though I suppose I might be making a false assumption here that is irresponsible. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showPrevMessage?topicID=327.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showNextMessage?topicID=327.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=327.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.polykarbon.com/bbsimage/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.emailToFriend?topicID=327.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.threadControl?topicID=327.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=327.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm32.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=327.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub25.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="polykarbonbbsfrm18">PK-BBS Rules and Regulations!<option value="polykarbonbbsfrm27">Board F.A.Q.s<option value="polykarbonbbsfrm3">News and Updates<option value